{"tid":1543449,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［全世界入黎望望］申請成為陪審員注意事項 ！","createTime":"2019-09-05T07:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T07:47:41.000Z","uid":267702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6afff4c76cb694b9f3357a65ada9ac340d80a39d","tid":1543449,"uid":267702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:40:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我岩先親自打去陪審團熱線 Fact Checked</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">- 任何人必須收到陪審團發出既確認信，先係成為合資格既陪審員！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">- 未收過 / 未收到信既，快 d 申請！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">*坊間流傳：大學畢業就會自動入到陪審團個 Pool ，呢個講法係錯既 ！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">申請成為陪審員流程如下 ： </span><br />\n<br />\n1/ 首先要打電話去 陪審員查詢熱線: 2825 4668, CHECK自己係唔係陪審員名單<br />\n2/ 如果唔係, 可以打去入境處 陪審團登記小組: 2829 3356<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n登記程序如下, 需要3樣文件, 如下: ( 即A+B+C )<br />\nA) 寫一封信, 內容話想登記成為陪審員, 包括要有:<br />\n- 中文 和 英文全名 (跟香港身份證一樣)<br />\n- 香港身份證號碼<br />\n- 記得要簽名<br />\n<br />\n----------------------範本如下:-------------------------<br />\n致: 陪審團登記小組<br />\n<br />\n本人 陳大文 (CHAN TAI MAN), HKID: A123456(7) 現想申請成為陪審員, 現附上表格ROP18 和 最高學歷文件副本, 如有問題, 請致電 9123 9123與本人聯絡.<br />\n<br />\n(你個簽名) <br />\n陳大文<br />\n2019-07-31<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\nB) 到入境處網站下載表格 (ROP18) 並填寫<br />\n- <a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/forms/forms/rop18.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fforms%2Fforms%2Frop18.html&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MIhk9ljSbOzVJb7ECUhiv3w%3D&h=56bd36e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/forms/forms/rop18.html</a><br />\n<br />\nC) 最高學歷文件副本<br />\n<br />\n請預備好 A)信, B) 表格ROP18 &amp; C) 最高學歷文件副本, 一併寄回到以下地址:<br />\n<br />\n香 港 灣 仔 告 士 打 道 七 號<br />\n入 境 事 務 大 樓 1 2 0 1 室<br />\n陪 審 團 登 記 小 組 收<br />\n<br />\n結果將會在大概一個月內以信面通知回覆"},{"pid":"cdd105ff5817cb96375ba379015be5c9de9456c5","tid":1543449,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:40:59.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff227212389e8922b5d8aa8fbc243b440aae66c4","tid":1543449,"uid":281388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:41:57.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"98b28209b70383876481db50127e7c3a035deb8d","tid":1543449,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"想問係咪最少要大學生先做得？"},{"pid":"4b30e089a5ea9aec2980720a6190cd7c64fceb30","tid":1543449,"uid":105501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98b28209b70383876481db50127e7c3a035deb8d","tid":1543449,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"想問係咪最少要大學生先做得？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:44:41.000Z","msg":"陪審員的資格<br />\n<br />\n出任陪審員是每一位合乎資格的香港居民應盡的責任。<br />\n<br />\n雖然出任陪審員有時會帶來不便，然而香港是一個法治社會，擁有透明度高的法律制度，陪審團所扮演的角色尤為重要，因此出任陪審員也是一種榮幸。<br />\n<br />\n任何具備下列條件的香港居民，均有資格出任陪審員：<br />\n<br />\n年滿21歲但未滿65歲；<br />\n精神健全而並無任何使其不能出任陪審員的情況如聽覺或視覺的損傷等；<br />\n品格良好，及<br />\n熟悉聆訊時所採用的語言&mdash; 即中文或英文（視乎個別情況而定）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.judiciary.hk/zh/jury/jury.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.judiciary.hk%2Fzh%2Fjury%2Fjury.html&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MIhk9ljSbOzVJb7ECUhiv3w%3D&h=cf89af43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.judiciary.hk/zh/jury/jury.html</a>"},{"pid":"43aff231354edb03f9574f38ee3d9b9dd91d1b06","tid":1